name: Out Of Somewhere (V)
Lore: 'When the ghost-like image of Obi-Wan failed to appear, another came out of the light to rescue Luke.',
Text: 'Use 1 Force to deploy (or retrieve) Lando from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If a battle just initiated, and your Lando defending alone at a site, his forfeit cannot be reduced, he adds one destiny to power (add 1 for each character and vehicle present), and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. (Immune to Sense.)',
